# Taranaki Harbour Board Empowering Act 1924Local Act1924 No 15

Date of assent6 November 1924

*   The words ""Taranaki Harbours Board"" were substituted, as from 1 September 1965, for the words ""Taranaki Harbour Board"" pursuant to section [15(2)][0] Taranaki Harbours Act 1965 (1965 No 4).

